map file index:
--------------

first line : x y z, sizes

second line : lites, #

third line : spheres cones cols, #

followed by map top z layer down

map objects:
	> 0 : empty
	> 1 : flat plane
	> 2 : vert l plane
	> 3 : vert r plane
	> 4 : corner
	> cam,x,y,z (vectors)
	> sphere,radius,color
	> col,radius,height,color
	> cone,radius,height,color
	> light,
